 Risk Management (Risk Register + Probability–Impact Matrix + Mitigation)
The Fitness Goal Tracking Dashboard project involves certain risks that may affect its successful completion. These risks are identified, analyzed, and mitigation strategies are proposed below.
Risk Register
Risk ID	Risk Description	Probability	Impact	Risk Level	Mitigation Strategy
R1	Delay in project completion	High	Medium	High	Create proper schedule and follow deadlines
R2	Bugs and errors in system	High	Medium	High	Perform regular testing and debugging
R3	Data loss or incorrect data storage	Medium	High	High	Implement data backup and validation
R4	Poor user interface design	Medium	Low	Medium	Take feedback and improve UI design
R5	Scope creep (adding extra features)	Low	Medium	Medium	Clearly define scope and avoid changes

